channel.title: [#317] Deobfuscated, Easily make a WebClient [Client made for Devo 1.1]
channel.description:
[CENTER]Welcome to my #317 Info inside the download.
Gameframe - 317 Sideicons - 420?
[COLOR=red]Known Bugs -[/COLOR] Wildy skull + wilderness level is not positioned correctly I don't believe
Make a webclient easily, do it yourself or follow Ric's Webclient Tutorial Note: I show a pic of me downloading cache, my client is ready to jar and upload, this one isn't - I'm not spoon feeding you.
[COLOR=DarkOrange]Download:[/COLOR] [url=http://runepalace.net/deob]http://runepalace.net/deob[/url]
^ [COLOR=DarkOrange]Direct Download[/COLOR] ^
[IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/2l0tb6.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/v65kjd.jpg[/img]
Like I said in the Title, this was released for my source Devolution 1.1.1 because that client fails.
Update: to change the sprite loading for Ric's tutorial, in Class30_sub20_sub1_sub1 change ./images/ do not search Sprites, you will not find /sprites
Feedback?[/CENTER]
